sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Free User
    participant FE as React<br/>AlertListPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>AlertListView
    participant SER as AlertListSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Enter search query (IP, keyword)
    FE->>API: GET /api/alerts/?search=192.168.1.100
    API->>DB: Alert.objects.filter(Q(source_ip__icontains) | Q(description__icontains))
    DB-->>API: Matching alerts
    API->>SER: AlertListSerializer(results, many=True)
    SER-->>API: Serialized search results
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {results: [...], count}
    FE-->>U: Display matching alerts
